<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - The Scorched Path</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="main-title"><%= translations?.[language]?.title || 'The three doors' %></h1>

  <div class="room-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="room-image">
        <img src="/images/a2_maze-dark-trap-1-right.png" alt="Trial by fire">
      </div>
      <div class="room-content">
        <div class="room-text">
    <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `The scorch marks suggest danger, but also that someone survived this path before. You choose the right passage.                                 
         <p> ahead, the passage continues into more darkness. You hear water dripping somewhere up ahead.</p>
            <p>Around a bend, you find another choice: three doorways. One door is made of iron. One is wooden. One is just an open archway with no door at all.</p>
            <p>Carved into the wall beside them, you notice ancient writing:</p>` %>
          </code>
          
          <div style="border: 2px solid #00ff00; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.05);">
            <code style="font-style: italic; text-align: center; display: block;">
              "The strongest stands but cannot yield,<br>
              The oldest falls to flame and field,<br>
              The wisest offers no shieldâ€”<br>
              What asks nothing is your safest path revealed."
            </code>
          </div>
            </div>

        <hr/>

        <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'This riddle is important - you need to think...' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-2-iron"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'Enter through the iron door' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-2-wood"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[1] || 'Enter through the wooden door' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-2-open"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[2] || 'Enter through the open archway' %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
